data_citing_statement: Author1, Author2 (2019): Example peat data v 1.0. Available online: https:\\zenodo.org\my-repository. DOI: 10.x23434/343.
data_abstract: Data set comprising FTIR-MIR spectra, element contents (C, N, O, H, S, P), bulk densities, and 210Pb activities for 40 peat samples from 4 peat cores taken at 2 sites in the United Kingdom.
data_keywords: peat; mid infrared spectra; Fourier transform infrared spectra; element content; bulk density; 210Pb activites; United Kingdom; peat core
